The two films "The Hunting Party" and "Moerderischer Frieden" are once again devoted to the war in the Balkans.
But the two didn’t have much conviction.
Either the concepts are fixed a lot on actions and shootings or both movies are too exciting.
Richard Gere with his "The Hunting Party" cannot help in this case either.
